Compile using ==> g++ main.cpp -o main -lstdc++fs -std=c++11

Benchmark Data Stream ==> ./main 1
Benchmark Buffered Stream => ./main 2
Benchmark Buffered Stream with fixed buffer size ==> ./main 3
Benchmark Memory Mapping ==> ./main 4
Benchmark External Merge Sort ==> ./main 5

Data files will be generated in the data/ directory and benchmark results in results/ directory.

All source code is located inside src/ and report (report.pdf) is present inside report/.
